Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.38,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:12.86,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Before I start talking about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:20.90,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I made an X-rated video\Nthat was a big hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:26.17,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\fscx120\pos(386.23,410.4)}Director: Yasuomi Umetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:26.04,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,A sponsor saw the video and asked my\Ncompany if we were interested in...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:28.64,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,...making an OVA for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:35.05,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The president of the company\Nasked me if I had any ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:41.72,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I had an idea that was for an\Naudience of all ages, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:47.03,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,...they were interested in\Nmaking an X-rated OVA.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:51.80,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I decided to do it because I\Nwas excited about making...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:58.14,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,...an original work, so it didn't\Nmatter if it was all-ages or X-rated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:03.61,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And, I gave them one plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,...the planning of "A Kite".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:16.22,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Originally "A Kite" was the\Nstory of a female assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:19.96,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,A female main character...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:23.63,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to make a piece that\Ndid not pander to a female audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:26.20,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And they also wanted to make\Nan action animation too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:30.50,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Even though there was the limit\Nof making an X-rated OVA...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:34.17,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,...I thought I would be able to\Nmake something I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.27,0:01:40.58,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So, I combined the ideas of a girl\Nassassin and an X-rated OVA.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:42.58,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That's how it started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:49.12,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, in terms of "A Kite"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:56.73,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It was my goal to create a piece where\NI could be in charge of all aspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:01.50,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, on a TV series,\Nall the work is divided.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:08.97,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The system of using individual talent to\Ncreate a series has been established.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:13.61,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But for an OVA, it is necessary\Nto express originality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:19.65,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It was easier for me to be in charge\Nof the many divisions of production.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:26.66,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I thought it was the most reasonable\Nway to communicate with the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:33.50,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,In order to visualize the sections\Nthat I had in my mind, for instance...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:38.04,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,...in the character\Ndesign or screenplay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:44.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,...it was better to do it myself rather\Nthan letting someone else do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:47.38,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't a burden at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:51.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It was a rather challenging\Nand enjoyable work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:57.39,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,This piece is pretty old...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:03:03.26,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,When the piece was finished, all the\Ntroubles turned into happy memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.06,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So I don't remember them well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:12.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The hardest parts of production were\Nthe screenplay and storyboards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:16.11,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,They were the most important\Nparts of the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:20.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Eighty percent of the quality of the\Nfinished piece depends on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:23.72,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That's how it is in animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:31.22,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The later processes, such as animation,\Nfinal line and photographing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:37.10,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,...fall into place if there is a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:40.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So the screenplay and\Nstoryboards are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:45.04,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I spent so much time working on\Nthe screenplay and storyboards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:50.08,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I spent most of the time\NI had working on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:56.28,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So that means the rest of the process\Nhad to work within a tight schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:04:00.29,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I remember that I gave\Neveryone trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:06.52,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,My next assignment is to make a\Nscreenplay and storyboards quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:08.46,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\fscx120\pos(386.23,410.4)}Director: Yasuomi Umetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:10.93,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,...but keep the piece's quality high.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:15.63,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I think if we could have finished the\Nstoryboards of "A Kite" earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:17.84,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,...the rest would have\Nworked smoother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:20.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So the quality could have been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Creators are greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:26.04,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,We always regret something\Nwhen a piece is finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:28.31,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,...and we try to do it\Nbetter for the next piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:31.08,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Since there was that\Nproblem in "A Kite "...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:34.85,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I thought that if I was more\Nefficient in the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:38.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I could have spent\Nmore time on the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.66,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The title was derived from...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:46.73,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well there is the girl assassin,\NSawa, and the boy assassin, Oburi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.53,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,These two are the main characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:53.37,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Since they are assassins,\Nthere has to be a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:56.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,They have to follow the client's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.74,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No one works individually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:00.98,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,They are connected by invisible strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:02.85,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm comparing them to a Kite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:05.88,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,There is a person who controls and\Nthere is a person who is controlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:09.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So, Sawa and Oburi exist on strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:15.56,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,In the end of this story, they\Ncut the Kite string and fly away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.60,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I decided to use the name\Nwith that connotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:34.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,If I say "this is how the story ends" or\N"it's how the character is going to be"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:36.15,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,that would be the end of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:45.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make the characters live\Nin people's hearts in their own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:54.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I want people to keep Oburi and\NSawa in their own imaginations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.63,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:06:08.41,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Intentionally, I look at everything around\Nmyself, from buildings to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:12.52,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's important to pay attention\Nto them all the time and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:15.89,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,absorb things that I can\Ncreate something from.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:17.86,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's like a mental drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:22.63,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,When I make my original characters,\NI take ideas from the drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:30.17,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Since I create my characters, I want\Nthem to exist as if they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:37.44,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Even though they are two dimensional,\NI try to create them with a presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:45.12,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,In order to create that, the characters\Nneed strong characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:53.73,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I combine many elements\Nand create a character.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:59.90,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The characters in "A Kite"\Nwere born in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:06.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, my reaction was like,\N"Please do whatever you want."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:10.01,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I don't want the director Rob Cohen\Nto be tied down by the OVA.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:12.54,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,He can have his own interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:21.39,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'd like him to keep the spirituality\Nof the OVA version of "A Kite".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:28.73,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But I want him to feel free to\Nexpress his own ideas and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:35.50,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,to make a live action movie of "A\NKite", interpreted through his own filter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:39.97,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I've always liked to draw\Nsince I was a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:44.48,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be a comic book artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:49.85,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I entered technical\Nschool for animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:54.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,My teacher used to be in\NTatsunoko Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:59.86,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,He told me the stories and showed me\Ndrawings from Tatsunoko Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:08:03.73,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\fscx120\pos(386.23,410.4)}Director: Yasuomi Umetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:05.86,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You get a lot of information about\Ncompanies in technical schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:10.10,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Information you've never heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:16.14,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I was curious and\Nintrigued by animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:21.88,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I was attracted by the fact that the\Npicture moves with sounds, like a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:26.85,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I've been immersed in\Nanimation since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I watch animations that\NI am curious about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:37.20,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,There are many people who record\Nanimations in my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:39.93,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And I borrow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:44.80,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I always hear people say, "This\Nis good." or "That's bad."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:50.44,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And I watch them and figure\Nout why it's bad or good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:09:01.65,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, in terms of animations, I\Nwatch them as a part of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:05.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I can't watch them objectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:11.96,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,If I watch the work of other professionals,\NI get jealous. Especially if it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:16.57,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm bitter when I say,\N"This is a good piece."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:20.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So it's hard for me to\Njudge it as an animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:25.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm part of the TV generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:32.48,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Because of where I grew up, I was\Ninfluenced by TV rather than movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:38.96,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,In the 1970's when Japanese TV series'\Nwere very popular, I began puberty...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:42.53,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I was hooked on the TV\Nshows of that period.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:51.04,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,They made a huge influence on my\Ntaste including my philosophy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:58.38,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,For example, detective shows,\Nsamurai shows and family shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:01.35,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,They became my core.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:08.12,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I started watching movies when I was\Ntwenty years old and moved Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:11.66,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Since then I was polished by movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:18.36,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But I think the TV shows from the\N70's are significant in my core.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:24.54,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,They were popular shows like\N"Taiyo ni Hoero" and "Daitokai".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:29.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,As a samurai show, "Monjiro's\NHissatsu" and others were in the 70's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:32.18,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Also, "Kizudarake no tenshi".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.52,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:44.86,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I would like to produce more\Nanimations as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:47.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your support.
